{"tid":1763731,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"美心集團爆料！！！大家小心中伏！！","createTime":"2019-11-30T14:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T08:13:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d5423848bcba9a0fd9bc5494d26b592f86c4a125","tid":1763731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"美心集團爆料！！！大家小心中伏！！跪求大家幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1763476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1763476</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JH7quX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JH7quX.png&h=92c67e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGp9DP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGp9DP6.png&h=61041be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有識嘅人係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑心集團</span></span>做<br />\n冬至就快到<br />\n大家千祈唔好去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全線惠康，Marketplace，3hreesixty</span>到拎呢張盆菜單張<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢係美心出嘅！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n美心呢次好醒，佢冇寫任何關於美心嘅資料<br />\n因為以往都有寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好中伏，繼續罷食罷買黑心集團</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好叫屋企人訂黑心</span><br />\n話就話新鮮製造，其實只係預先包裝之後叮翻熟<br />\n運送過程亦都好易變壞，分分鐘食死人！<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家推出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf719b396c3cf2c5a035fd09c8fc49a74982012","tid":1763731,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"我強烈要求 黃大仙今日個集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1763740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1763740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90275a8e105486258df8d594093ad44f299ed938","tid":1763731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897198e0c9047ab7ad488200582135aac92a0780","tid":1763731,"uid":98899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"其實成個集團不嬲互相輸送<br />\n買開都知係美心做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aea001072e6108be6e3df26981f011c055e44ec","tid":1763731,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"做咩開2個po啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53a84c116a561d6cb026bcb20b36dd187808094","tid":1763731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aea001072e6108be6e3df26981f011c055e44ec","tid":1763731,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"做咩開2個po啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"吹水台邊個睇到"},{"pid":"8751c685e1dafbfef3991f05005112c2c11912dd","tid":1763731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28694d23309e0754e97873c9223e65f34464a942","tid":1763731,"uid":36833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cef2a6cdb89c2ce6087df75ea7b7b74030daf79","tid":1763731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b114eaae1805924f316d11f3e74d559824bb0671","tid":1763731,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c4f967b5d7239b50788d803c20cd002859edfec","tid":1763731,"uid":222251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:31:52.0